---------------------------------------------------------------
   Instructions for adding r-function values to pre-existing
         HBOOK column-wise Ntuple created by ESPACE
----------------------------------------------------------------

1) Edit the file ~/mceep/cmn/ntu_user.cmn (see that file for
   instructions).
2) Run ~/mceep/utilities/mceep_util (option 5) from the directory
   containing your input ESPACE HBOOK file.  This will generate
   a file called "skeleton" in that directory.
3) Execute the script ~/mceep/utilities/build_cwn_include from 
   the directory containing your input HBOOK file.
4) Run ~/mceep/utilities/mceep_util (option 6) from the directory
   containing your input ESPACE HBOOK file.
